{
  "text": "I had already determined to exclude him from these workings. I had only determined to let him read the material. The only other thing is that I have noticed that within the material as it exists now, there is a certain statement which will allow him to understand who I believe Spectra really was. It seems my duty to remove this from his knowledge to preserve the same free will that you attempted to preserve by not defining the origin of Spectre, his contact and misery. Am I correct? I am Ra. This is a matter for your discretion.",
